# Diabetes Prediction using SPSS Modeler

This project uses Logistic Regression to predict diabetes using the Pima Indians Diabetes Dataset.

## Tools Used
- IBM SPSS Modeler
- Excel

## Workflow
1. Data Import
2. Type Node
3. Partition Node
4. Select Node
5. Logistic Regression
6. Model Evaluation

## Dataset Features
- Pregnancies
- Glucose
- Blood Pressure
- BMI
- Age
- Outcome
